@startuml Sequence_RealtimeAudio
title Real-Time Audio Pipeline

participant "Provider Agent" as Provider
participant "Twilio\nMedia Stream" as Twilio
participant "SpeechToText\nStream" as STT
participant "Deepgram" as DG
participant "NegotiationAgent" as Agent
participant "Claude API" as Claude
participant "TextToSpeech\nEngine" as TTS
participant "ElevenLabs" as EL

Provider -> Twilio: speaks (analog audio)
Twilio -> STT: audio chunk (mulaw 8kHz WS)
STT -> DG: forward audio (WebSocket)

DG --> STT: interim transcript
DG --> STT: final transcript
STT --> Agent: TranscriptEvent{text, isFinal}

Agent -> Agent: updateContext(turn)
Agent -> Claude: generate response\n(history + strategy + state)
Claude --> Agent: response text

Agent -> TTS: speakIntoCall(text)
TTS -> EL: POST /text-to-speech/stream\n(text, voice, ulaw_8000)
EL --> TTS: audio chunks (streaming)
TTS -> Twilio: media payload (mulaw WS)
Twilio -> Provider: synthesized speech

note over STT, TTS
  Total latency budget: <2 seconds
  Deepgram STT:  ~300ms
  Claude API:    ~800ms
  ElevenLabs:    ~400ms
  Network/buffer: ~300ms
end note

@enduml
